Loopback.titleText:
IMG2IMG ONLY

Params:
loops (int) //def: 8
denoising_strength_change_factor (decimal, 0.90-1.10) //def: 0.99
append_interrogation (enum, str: ["None","CLIP","DeepBooru"]) //def: None

Prompt matrix.titleText:
Params:
put_at_start (bool): expect pipe (|) delimited options at start of prompt //def: false
different_seeds (bool): use different seeds for each picture //def: false
prompt_type (enum, str: ["positive","negative"]) //def: "positive"
variations_delimiter (enum, str ["comma", "space"] //def: "comma"
margin_size (int): px margin value //def: 2

X/Y/Z plot.titleText:
Params:
x_type (int): index of axis type (see below) //def: 3
x_values (mixed, str) //def: "0.00-0.99 [4]"
y_type (int) //def: 4
y_values (mixed, str) //def: "5-30 [4]"
z_type (int) //def: 6
z_values (mixed, str) //def: "2.5-12.5 [4]"
draw_legend (bool): return grid of all images //def: false
include_lone_images (bool): return individual images //def: true
include_subgrids (bool) //def: false
no_fixed_seeds (bool): use different seeds for each picture //def: false
margin_size (int): grid margins in px //def: 2

Available axis types:
0: Nothing
1: Seed
2: Var. seed
3: Var. strength
4: Steps
5: Hires steps (txt2img only)
6: CFG Scale
7: Prompt S/R
8: Prompt order
9: Sampler (txt2img only)
10: Sampler (img2img only)
11: Checkpoint Name
12: Sigma Churn
13: Sigma min
14: Sigma max
15: Sigma noise
16: Eta
17: Clip skip
18: Denoising
19: Hires upscaler (txt2img only)
20: Cond. Image Mask Weight (img2img only)
21: VAE
22: Styles
